Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Intro}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.20,0:00:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai, we'll be on a family trip \Nto the hot springs during Golden Week.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have that time off.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.24,0:00:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not go on holiday somewhere while you're free? {## I need a word for "don't have to go to work"}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.21,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.05,0:00:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what she suggested, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.92,0:00:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been nonstop gaming \Nfor about seventy-two hours since.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the last one?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That unnecessary rhythmic flourish...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.78,0:01:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Sakurai!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}knew{\i0} it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.63,0:02:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free today? \NI mean, you totally are, right?
Comment: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:38.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.05,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just pop in unannounced and spout rubbish.{you pop over unannounced and spitting whatever you wanna say}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.14,0:02:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I figured I'd drop by since loners like you \Nalways hole up playing games when they're off work.{Well, you're off work, and I figured \Na loner like you would be home gaming}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And wow, turns out I was right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no words.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.48,0:02:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So here I am to hang out with you, \Nmy senior but above all else, friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.61,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Great news, ye?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop the condescending tone, it pisses me off.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna play Doramon GO™ on the go?{"go out and play"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's still a game!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.24,0:03:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a big spawning event during Golden Week. {## double-check what term is used in Pokemon GO}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's catch 'em all—together!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have it, too.{"I have the app, all right."}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.13,0:03:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Buuut?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But playing alone is too embarrassing, so I didn't.{But I was too embarrassed to play alone.}{"so I didn't" at the end}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.17,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is! Man, I can read you like a book!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you turn it off?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's play together!{Let's playy together}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.72,0:03:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talk about a major pain in the behind, \NThough we {\i0}do{\i1} have holiday...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Sakurai...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to die of boredom, so sure, I'll play along.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a Lousy Cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this out, Sakurai!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If looks could kill, \Nyours would be the most lethal.{YABAI}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gamed too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.30,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Being all scowly's one thing, but walking around \Nwith that face on top of that?{"You are all scowly to begin with, and now walking with that face"}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's gonna report you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind not slowly backing away like that?{"backing away casually"}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But hey, you sure seem to be catching a lot!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A lotta gorillas, that is.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just one after another.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.02,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, my eyes sting. Screen's too bright.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.45,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! How's going glasses shopping sound?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ami, that you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.17,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancy running into you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.30,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So your eyes hurt \Nfrom playing games too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, he'll be Doramon GO™-ing \Nstraight to the police station!{OG: If this keeps up, \Nhe'll be Doramon Go-ing to lockup.}{## tfw can't think of anything funny}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna have a Doramon GO™ at it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.14,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai, you've done nothing but play video games \Nwhile we were at the hot springs?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.44,0:05:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bet he'd still be going at it \Nif I didn't come knocking!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No denying that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.49,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she's here anyway, why not \Nget Ami to be your glassistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My glassistant?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you're looking for?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this hermit gaming-addict here \Nis in dire need of a specific item:
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Computer glasses!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.96,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the ones that cut down \Non blue light from LCD displays?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,These bad boys are supposed to \Nkeep your eyes from getting strained!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted a pair myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.18,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm. Might be good for long gaming sessions.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.85,0:05:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! The lenses are a faint yellow.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're like thin sunglasses, eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You really rock the glasses look!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you try these on real quick?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice! Should we try on some others?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Totes!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, which ones?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.54,Alt,,0,0,0,,How about these?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like I'm some kind of dress-up doll.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are {\i1}perfect{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.79,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.96,0:06:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! It hides your glare so well that \Nyou almost look normal!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said I don't look normal?!{who has the glare mug?!"}{## changing the subject here because it sounds better imo}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.88,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably wear \Nthose at work and school, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about these?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you find {\i1}those{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Et tu, Ami? Why join in making fun of me?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow. This is priceless. Can I take a pic?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.32,0:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookie here... or y'know what, don't.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop laughing. It's hard to aim!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.66,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Try, uh, these on next, Sakurai!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.04,0:06:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already in tears!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.55,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Combined with your natural fierce look, \Nyou get the ultimate mafioso look!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you'd assassinate somebody with a fibre wire!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.89,0:06:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Or like you were dominating the criminal underworld!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.10,0:07:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw on a white coat and \Nyou'd nail the mad scientist look!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.56,0:07:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.86,0:07:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What shelf were these on? \NI'm putting them back!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai, please! Just once!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.86,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Brush your hair back with \Nthose little round glasses on!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once, I swear!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.29,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll turn into an \Nembarrassingly tropey character!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you {\i1}want{\i0} from me?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry! This is the final pair.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,These were a serious choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.30,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now make a fist.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your arm.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your mouth a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayyyyy-oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, that was the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better pick out \Nyour own glasses there, Hana.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.99,0:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, which ones?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,These might suit you, don't you think?{"these might suit you, don't you think? "}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.25,0:08:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I do dig a pink frame...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But red is rad!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.21,0:08:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out, Sakurai. \NDoesn't Hana look good in glasses?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya think?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You look dumber, strangely enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Strangely enough"?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.19,0:08:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I was complimenting you earlier!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you called me a mafioso! \NThat makes it a wash, you dolt!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.95,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Picky, picky! \NThat's what you are, you know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone's gotta know what they are, it'd be you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's always {\i1}you{\i0} who's \Ngetting angry at everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You asked for it, dumbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.38,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a dumbass calls others dumbasses, dumbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'd be a dumbass too then, right, dumbass?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.51,0:08:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.51,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Doesn't count if you said it first, \Ndumbass! Dumbass! Dumbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.68,0:09:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. They're always like that.
Comment: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:09.02,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.48,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed out on getting glasses, \Nand it's all your fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Got a Lousy Cat Dandy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.53,0:09:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} just {\i1}had{\i0} to start something.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Gorilla.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.03,0:09:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't dump the blame on me \Njust 'cause you're older.{not cause but "Don't dump the blame on me, you are the older one " in terms of, be a bigger man kind of meaning, or like, be nice to your juniors etc, or you should be the one acting his shit together}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's power harassment.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I got a Lousy Cat Genius this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.67,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly it's {\i1}your{\i0} fault, because {\i1}you{\i0} started it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing but Gorillas.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See, {\i1}your{\i0} problem is—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.56,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nechst Station. Nechst Station.{I love this ahahah, I think you'd get it but tsugi no eki=next station}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lot of people getting on.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.40,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But with this game, the more people \Naround you, the higher the monster spawn rate.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See? A Lousy Cat Cyborg!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Still Gorillas here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how much do you like gorillas?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.71,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't. {\i1}They{\i0} like {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as long as we get where we're going.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Andenechst Station.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Andefallo-Wing Station.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's crazy crowded.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.35,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right—there's a soccer match \Nat a nearby stadium.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, huh-huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Something incredibly soft...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.12,0:10:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.12,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Can't really help it in all this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.29,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad—and at this rate, \Nit'll get {\i1}really{\i0} bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't budge!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I just going to have to grin and bear it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.85,0:11:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of something else \Nand pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sakurai?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's n-nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's {\i1}that{\i0} doing here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta get my mind on something else, pronto...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}fine{\i0}. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are traps everywhere I turn!{astolfo says hi- aria}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see nothing. I hear nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I turn my consciousness inward.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.63,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him? \NHe got so quiet all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh—his eyelashes are really long.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,His face is {\i1}so close{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.93,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture it—now! A clear blue sky!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.43,0:11:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like one of those \Nwall-pound things, huh? Ha ha...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A vast field, stretching \Nas far as the eye can see!{wow windows xp background -aria}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.56,0:11:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your arm tired? Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.40,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystal-clear, unclouded water, \Nits surface like a mirror!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.28,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do this. I can make it through!{"I've gotta make it through"}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.00,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With my eyes closed and my ears dulled, \Nmy other senses are heighten—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.51,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, uh, Sakurai... Thanks for earli—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.39,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.52,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he out cold—on his feet?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The door is closing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is our stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai? Sakurai!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... Now what?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait—what time is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.09,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a ton of calls from Uzaki.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And... one of these.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.60,0:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that's{\i0} what happened during...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...during Golden Week?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No laughing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.53,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I blacked out before it got to that point.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.04,0:13:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If {\i1}she{\i0} made me feel that way, \NI figured I'd be better off unconscious!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, can he just turn his \Nconsciousness off and on at will?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he, a ninja? Spooky.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.80,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't worry too much about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.72,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're young—you should be more carefree.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.68,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm sure my Ami \Nis hanging out with boys.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With boys?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.32,0:14:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.21,0:14:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To think something so hilar—er, \Nterrible happened to you afterward!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You were going to say "hilarious"!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was unfortunate.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow up with Hana.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.64,0:14:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she's the one who invited you along.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.49,0:14:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on, \Nbut I'm not going to engage. Too much trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to this, Sakurai.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's{\i0} engaging {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking at the calendar when it hit me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.88,0:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no holidays in June.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.09,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And {\i1}that's{\i0} why you're so down?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got weekends off.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.18,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But the more and longer breaks \Nthe better, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Greedy much?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A three-day break really winds you up!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.56,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I get depressed thinking \Nabout this weather sticking around
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for another month.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.07,0:15:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. But after the rainy \Nseason comes summer break.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But not before exams.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.99,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go have fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.25,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do that, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.25,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How about next weekend?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.75,0:15:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't startle me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} startled {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This same old loner of a senior, \Nsuggesting we go somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.51,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell must be frozen over! Completely frozen over! \NAnd now I know why it's raining!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because {\i1}you{\i0} say such weird stuff! Ugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make heads or tails \Nof this mixed-up conversation!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.86,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't work for you, then never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... good.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.74,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So... is there someplace you had in mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.32,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know: How about an outing by train?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai, your face is all red.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. No trains.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do you mind if I just \Nthrow something together?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.51,0:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! I can't wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one frightening laugh.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's not every day that {\i1}you{\i0} invite {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.69,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I felt bad for what \Nhappened over Golden Week.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.36,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I told Ami, \Nshe said I should follow up with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you mad?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You totally are.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the slightest.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, if I were mad, it'd be a big deal!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.51,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pouring. Forget going out in this.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she's still home...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.48,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to call you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.24,0:17:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured if it was gonna rain anyway, \NI may as well play games at your place.{"downpour rain"}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.62,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd cook, so I did a little shopping, \Nand it started raining harder...{I thought I'd cook while I have the chance..."
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time I left the supermarket, \Nit was a total disaster.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the sentiment, \Nbut don't go overboard.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.88,0:17:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow your shower? \NOh... and a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, I shouldn't have worn my favorite shirt.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to join me?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go already!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.69,0:18:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I'm soaked clear through to my undies!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! TMI!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This shirt is {\i1}ginormous{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.91,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just get lunch started \Nbefore we start playing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.42,0:18:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any good cookware, \Nso I'm giving you my old pot.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.80,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's incredibly nice of you. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,First...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Need help?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.35,0:18:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no cook. How about washing these veggies?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awfully obedient today, Sakurai.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.86,0:19:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that everything's been \Ngoing wrong for you today, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.11,0:19:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine—I'm a good cook.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.95,0:19:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you couldn't taste the porridge \NI made for you when you were sick,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's a little score-settling in the mix.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.50,0:19:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry I said that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.63,0:19:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My cooking will have your \Nunsophisticated palate {\i1}moaning{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, you've gone a step too far.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What game do you want to play?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.27,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You downloaded Meowcraft! Let's play that!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work together to build \Nsomething totally out-there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.90,0:19:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too perfect a way for \Na college student to waste a day off.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.87,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to be a useless college student?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you've been one all along.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! That was fun!{"That's what I'd call a gaming night"}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.33,0:20:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was asking too much \Nto finish our build in one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}did{\i0} get torn down a few times.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.54,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can just work on it \Nthe next time you're over.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.54,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The... next time?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.42,0:20:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with the scary laugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.89,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the curry pot in \Nthe fridge just like that, 'kay?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.31,0:21:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.36,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll taste even better after sitting overnight.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.65,0:21:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've heard that. Is it true?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.45,0:21:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it sit overnight and the roux \Nsoaks into the meat and veggies,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.87,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,which release their umami components—amino \Nacids, sugars—into the roux!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.75,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you get a richer \Numami flavor all through the curry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.46,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry I asked.{"TLDR" would suit better lol}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Though today's was already plenty good.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.73,0:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You said "the next time"... How about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.15,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, to pick up where we left off today? \NSure. God knows I'm free.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.91,0:21:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's hang out again, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.46,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... wait—what?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.50,0:22:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I seem to have \Nleft my pass at your place.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.18,0:22:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}so{\i0} disorganized.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.15,0:23:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Episode 5: I Want to Meddle \Nin My Friend's Business!"
